in \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15287,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/22\/eat-walking-drink-standing\/","url_meta":{"origin":29323,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Manners: Concession to eat walking, drink standing","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 22, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: In the lifetime of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, we would eat while walking and drink while standing. Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1880 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064f\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0627 \u0646\u064e\u0623\u0652\u0643\u064f\u0644\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0649 \u0639\u064e\u0647\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38821,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/02\/18\/punished-qabr-urine\/","url_meta":{"origin":29323,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Tahara: Punishment in grave for uncleanliness with urine","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 18, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of A